My Shortcuts Extension for Chrome
Quickly access your favorite Google™ Web Apps: Gmail™, Contacts, Calendar, Docs and other Google™ services, or create a new email, event, document, spreadsheet or presentation.

UPDATE (2.5.1): Added option to use new Google Contacts™ (within Gmail™) interface.

UPDATE (2.5): Added New Google Doc™ format, added more custom links, ability to remove Google Apps™ Url from top of popup, fixed new calendar url.

Thanks for your support!

